<p id="mwApY">In the ostensibly <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Covariance_and_contravariance_of_vectors#Informal_usage" title="Covariance and contravariance of vectors" id="mwApc">covariant</a> (relativistically invariant) <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Dirac_equation" title="Dirac equation" id="mwApg">Dirac equation</a>, and in <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Natural_units" title="Natural units" id="mwApk">natural units</a>, this becomes:</p>
<dl id="mwApo"><dd id="mwAps"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt423" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"(-i\\gamma^\\mu\\partial_\\mu + m) \\psi = 0\\,"}}' id="mwApw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle (-i\gamma ^{\mu }\partial _{\mu }+m)\psi =0\,}">
