rologia</a></i>. <b id="mwA-w">47</b> (3): L5–L8. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Bibcode" title="Bibcode" id="mwA-0">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2010Metro..47L...5L" id="mwA-4">2010Metro..47L...5L</a>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwA-8">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1088%2F0026-1394%2F47%2F3%2FL01" id="mwA_A">10.1088/0026-1394/47/3/L01</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwA_E">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwA_I">2013-09-15</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Metrologia&amp;rft.atitle=Comments+on+recent+proposals+for+redefining+the+mole+and+kilogram&amp;rft.volume=47&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=L5-L8&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1088%2F0026-1394%2F47%2F3%2FL01&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2010Metro..47L...5L&amp;rft.aulast=Leonard&amp;rft.aufirst=B.P.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2F0026-1394%2F47%2F3%2FL01%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMass" class="Z3988" about="#mwt141" id="mwA_M"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt141" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA_Q"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-30" id="cite_note-30"><a href="./Mass#cite_ref-30" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-30" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt142" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite journal\n","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"title":{"wt":"Some reflections on the proposed redefinition of the unit for the amount of substance and of o