 integer.)</small><br/></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%">Example</th><td class="navbox-list navbox-odd" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px"><div style="padding:0em 0.25em">Quantity <i>acceleration</i> = <span class="texhtml "><i>l</i><sup>1</sup><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><b><span typeof="mw:Entity">·</span></b><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><i>t</i><sup><span typeof="mw:Entity">−</span>2</sup></span>, <span class="nowrap">dim <i>acceleration</i> = L<sup>1</sup><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><b><span typeof="mw:Entity">·</span></b><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>T<sup><span typeof="mw:Entity">−</span>2</sup></span><br/>possible units: <span class="nowrap">m<sup>1</sup><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><b><span typeof="mw:Entity">·</span></b><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>s<sup><span typeof="mw:Entity">−</span>2</sup></span>, <span class="nowrap">km<sup>1</sup><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><b><span typeof="mw:Entity">·</span></b><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>Ms<sup><span typeof="mw:Entity">−</span>2</sup></span>, etc.</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%">See also</th><td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px"><div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
